reviewText: I bought this for White Comanche with William Shatner playing dual roles. The video quality of that particular movie is amazingly poor in this set. With collections like these I expect VHS quality or somewhat worse given my experiences with similar sets but, man, really lousy quality video.
No, there was nothing about it that was enjoyable.
I love westerns and especially ones with Sam Elliot and/or Tom Selik
I only put 5 stars because of the actor involved.  Does anyone including Amazon know what movies are in this DVD?
